text: Anoplolepis nuptialis is a species of ant. It belongs to the family Formicidae. It is endemic to South Africa. ==References== * Social Insects Specialist Group 1996. Anoplolepis nuptialis. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 31 July 2007. Category:Ants
title: Anoplolepis nuptialis
